    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索梦境这一件事本就是一场险途。这里既有久违的挚友, 也有噬人的噩梦。握紧你手中的“伞刃”, 凭借勇气穿梭于这片由记忆残片构建的诡谲世界——每一步都踏在摇摇欲坠的往事边缘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >类只狼战斗</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >节奏紧凑的魂类对决, 以格挡与反击作为核心战斗机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用<strong>闪避</strong>与<strong>弹反</strong>，引爆敌人所积累的架势！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/5d50116c2015effa5e27decee98927e8.poster.avif?t=1771269095\" aria-label=\"The Feral Cat\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/5d50116c2015effa5e27decee98927e8.webm?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/5d50116c2015effa5e27decee98927e8.mp4?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直面传说级魔王</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战二十余位强敌！在一次次登堂入室的生死交锋中，凭本事改写结局，踏过巍峨对手与独特机制构成的试炼，逼近尼洛的极限。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/458e618ce73fc28b379c0b2fd76cdb49.poster.avif?t=1771269095\" aria-label=\"The Deadline\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/458e618ce73fc28b379c0b2fd76cdb49.webm?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/458e618ce73fc28b379c0b2fd76cdb49.mp4?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/934a522a1be3fe17edb77c2642d211b3.poster.avif?t=1771269095\" aria-label=\"The Handler\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/934a522a1be3fe17edb77c2642d211b3.webm?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/934a522a1be3fe17edb77c2642d211b3.mp4?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁多样武器！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并精通 4 种强力副武器与多样致命技能，塑造你的战斗流派。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中可获得梦境碎片，开辟全新战斗机制、解谜思路与探索路径。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/c81cd6fd11fca55157aee7d454dd482b.poster.avif?t=1771269095\" aria-label=\"Secondhand Equipment\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/c81cd6fd11fca55157aee7d454dd482b.webm?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/c81cd6fd11fca55157aee7d454dd482b.mp4?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索支离破碎的梦境</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追索那些游走于光影之间的奇异身影，寻回与尼洛在清醒世界亦牵系不散的旧友……</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越美好与恐怖交织的手工雕琢的梦境，挖掘深埋的真相。你是否已准备好直面扭曲的记忆，拼凑破碎的过往残片？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/090438f11480417e9eb04efeed27dbe1.poster.avif?t=1771269095\" aria-label=\"Walk\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/090438f11480417e9eb04efeed27dbe1.webm?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3240610/extras/090438f11480417e9eb04efeed27dbe1.mp4?t=1771269095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
